node.text: Well.  It’s official.  I’m a college mom.  I’m so proud of you son!!!!!! College whew 😥 I mean I knew you’d make it here.  I hope you grow, learn, make new friends here in ATL SHAWTY ♥️ I love you.  Of all the things I’ve ever done wrong in this life you were there with me in the struggle always and you’re proof that I did ONE THING right (that’s you) 💋 love you. Gotta blast 🚀 and cry.  BRB. #GSU #panthers
